- PHP 8.2+, strict_types=1 everywhere
- No framework — PSR-4 App\ → src/
- Bootstrap 5, jQuery 3.7 frontend, MySQL 8.0+ InnoDB utf8mb4_unicode_ci

## Database
- Use `App\Core\Database` PDO wrapper with named params
- Table names: `DB::CUSTOMERS` constants only
- Always `organization_id` scoping, never `SELECT *`

## Architecture
- Controller → Service → Repository → Model (readonly DTO)
- Throw `App\Exception\*`, never `die()`/`exit()` in src/
- CSRF on every POST, permissions via `granted('action', $module_id)`

## Do NOT
- package.json, Node.js, PHP frameworks, SELECT *, @ suppression
- Comments unless asked, markdown docs unless asked
- Hard deletes (use is_active=0)

## Layout
- No inline CSS — use `haipulse-dashboard-compat.css`
- Page header: flex, space-between, title left + buttons right
- `.content-inner` direct child of `.content-wrapper`, copyright at bottom
